description:
The Shelbourne - Series 1, Episode 6




The hotel begins a multimillion-euro refurbishment of the bedrooms. The builders are given five days to transform eight rooms, which will be inspected by managers Alan Mahoney and Agnes Keogh. Their approval is not easily won, and everybody begins to feel the pressure. Meanwhile, JD Flynn and the front-of-house team enjoy a team-building day trip to a tree-top obstacle course. Last in the series.




Original Air Date: 22-Aug-2014
